{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"VRPose","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose\"><code>VRPose</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/angularAcceleration\"><code>angularAcceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/angularVelocity\"><code>angularVelocity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/linearAcceleration\"><code>linearAcceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/linearVelocity\"><code>linearVelocity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/orientation\"><code>orientation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/position\"><code>position</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebVR API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/displayId\"><code>Gamepad.displayId</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/activeVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.activeVRDisplays</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.getVRDisplays()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayCapabilities\"><code>VRDisplayCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayEvent\"><code>VRDisplayEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters\"><code>VREyeParameters</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRFieldOfView\"><code>VRFieldOfView</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRFrameData\"><code>VRFrameData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRLayerInit\"><code>VRLayerInit</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters\"><code>VRStageParameters</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div></div>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>VRPose</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API</a> represents the state of a VR sensor at a given timestamp (which includes orientation, position, velocity, and acceleration information.)</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API</a>&nbsp; 中的&nbsp;<strong><code>VRPose</code></strong> 接口表示在一个给定的时间戳中，一个 VR 传感器的状态（包括了方向、位置、速度和加速度信息）。</p>\n\n<p>This interface is accessible through the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/getPose\"><code>VRDisplay.getPose()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> and&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/getImmediatePose\"><code>VRDisplay.getImmediatePose()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> methods.</p>\n\n<p>这个接口能通过&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/getPose\"><code>VRDisplay.getPose()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 和 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/getImmediatePose\"><code>VRDisplay.getImmediatePose()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法访问</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"vrpose.timestamp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timeStamp</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the current time stamp of the system — a monotonically increasing value useful for determining if position data has been updated, and what order updates have occured in.</dd>\n <dd>返回当前系统的时间戳。此单调递增的值可以有助于确定位置数据是否有更新，以及更新的顺序。</dd>\n <dt id=\"vrpose.position_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/position\"><code>VRPose.position</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the position of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> at the current <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a> as a 3D vector</dd>\n <dd>以三维向量的形式返回当前时间戳 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a> &nbsp;时&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> &nbsp;的位置信息。</dd>\n <dt id=\"vrpose.linearvelocity_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/linearVelocity\"><code>VRPose.linearVelocity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the linear velocity of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> at the current <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a>, in meters per second.</dd>\n <dd>返回当前时间戳 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a> &nbsp;时&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> &nbsp;的线速度，单位为米/秒。</dd>\n <dt id=\"vrpose.linearacceleration_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/linearAcceleration\"><code>VRPose.linearAcceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the linear acceleration of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> at the current <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a>, in meters per second per second.</dd>\n <dd>返回当前时间戳 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a> &nbsp;时&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> &nbsp;的线加速度，单位为米/平方秒。</dd>\n <dt id=\"vrpose.orientation_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/orientation\"><code>VRPose.orientation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the orientation of the sensor at the current <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a>, as a quarternion value.</dd>\n <dd>以四元数的形式返回当前时间戳 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a> &nbsp;时传感器的方向，</dd>\n <dt id=\"vrpose.angularvelocity_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/angularVelocity\"><code>VRPose.angularVelocity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the angular velocity of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> at the current <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a>, in radians per second.</dd>\n <dd>返回当前时间戳 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a> &nbsp;时&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> &nbsp;的角速度，单位为弧度/秒。</dd>\n <dt id=\"vrpose.angularacceleration_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/angularAcceleration\"><code>VRPose.angularAcceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the angular acceleration of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> at the current <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a>, in meters per second per second.</dd>\n <dd>返回当前时间戳 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp\"><code>VRPose.timestamp</code></a> &nbsp;时&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a> &nbsp;的角加速度，单位为弧度/平方秒。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">TBD.</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#interface-vrpose\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">VRPose</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">Unknown</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.VRPose","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API homepage</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"http://mozvr.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MozVr.com</a> — demos, downloads, and other resources from the Mozilla VR team.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The VRPose interface of the WebVR API represents the state of a VR sensor at a given timestamp (which includes orientation, position, velocity, and acceleration information.)","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"VRPose","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"VRPose","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"VRPose","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/vrpose","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/vrpose/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose","title":"VRPose"}],"pageTitle":"VRPose - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}